---
description: Require DoneProof receipts before agent handoff
alwaysApply: false
---

Before handing work back:

1. Create or update `.doneproof/receipts/latest.json`.
2. Run `doneproof check --receipt .doneproof/receipts/latest.json`.
3. Run `doneproof report --receipt .doneproof/receipts/latest.json`.
4. Use `awaiting_review`, `blocked`, or `failed`.
5. Do not claim approval. The receipt makes review easier; it does not replace review.
